&lt;li&gt;Engineer Intern (E.I.) certification (passed FE exam), preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AutoCAD Civil 3D, including preparation of site plans, grading plans, and utility layouts.&lt;/li&gt;
