&lt;p&gt;Are you an experienced &lt;strong&gt;Construction Inspector&lt;/strong&gt; with a strong background in public works and infrastructure projects? Lumos &amp;amp; Associates is seeking a detail-oriented professional to support critical infrastructure development throughout the Sacramento region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for someone who thrives in the field and has hands-on experience inspecting water, sewer, storm drain, concrete, and transportation/roadway projects for public agencies.&lt;/p&gt;
